TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed MsoCondition extends System.Enum

Docs.summary: Defines the condition for comparison between a file and a specified property in a file search.

remarks.para: Used to get or set the Condition property of the PropertyTest object. PropertyTest is part of the FileSearch object model. The behavior of FileSearch corresponds to the interactive behavior you see in the Finddialog box, which you open from the Tools menu in the application's Open dialog box (File menu).
